Package: heatmaps
Title: Flexible Heatmaps for Functional Genomics and Sequence Features
Version: 0.99.11
Date: 18-01-2016
Author: Malcolm Perry <mgperry32@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Malcolm Perry <mgperry32@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3)
